{"tid":527581,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"星加坡根本係狗國家 請立即停止吹奏","createTime":"2018-01-12T21:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-04T15:20:42.000Z","uid":130406,"like":253,"dislike":58,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"898e7887ea1eac45f19553459ac3c5ef91cffbe0","tid":527581,"uid":130406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T21:01:40.000Z","msg":"星加坡簡直係狗國家<br />\n<br />\n同美國frd同時為錢又要媚共走去轉做殘體字但又同台灣曖味<br />\n<br />\n香港想同東盟簽自由貿易協定又一直搞搞震眼紅<br />\n<br />\n明眀亞洲國家又滿口番文無晒靈魂<br />\n有咩原因亞洲人會為左學一種歐洲語言就拋棄自己文化自己根 唔通學外語係咁難?<br />\n個腦裝唔晒? 人地鄰居馬來西亞個個又馬拉文粵語華語客家話福建話  屌你淨講英文變成垃圾Singlish難聽到死<br />\n<br />\n星加坡狗也不屌 香港只不過畀中共騎住佢至上到位獨立到佢實收皮"},{"pid":"ea0f6359e857a60c81ab94ef98f3a2dc33b2c88d","tid":527581,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T21:05:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5535700e63412d048add4c2529bf8c9ac1078a","tid":527581,"uid":42691,"like":48,"dislike":6,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T21:27:01.000Z","msg":"學曬你既野宜家好景過你"},{"pid":"96998a9c6fa9fe827c74140910490e9abcdd4772","tid":527581,"uid":123456,"like":22,"dislike":15,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T21:39:38.000Z","msg":"冇民主人權已經係死罪啦"},{"pid":"c9d0d1f040c0d87ff138495a9d0279d45f3d2bd2","tid":527581,"uid":52215,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:27:16.000Z","msg":"見工如果阿頭坡佬<br />\n一定唔撚做"},{"pid":"a784455385ddcc6ac64a27a89bbd625679f2fee5","tid":527581,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:29:21.000Z","msg":"兩頭dildo"},{"pid":"d47ff770e6315451d10addb9f527e60bdb6f7f11","tid":527581,"uid":35266,"like":45,"dislike":4,"score":41,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-13T00:49:59.000Z","msg":"但連登仔一直自豪既英國殖民地色彩<br />\n新加坡保留得好過香港好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcf3c7add3c53d4047b551a687839fb3a95f86e4","tid":527581,"uid":77092,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyT